{"tid":2197490,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"驚方聲稱被捕人士沽空壹傳媒","createTime":"2020-09-10T15:48:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-11T04:02:04.000Z","uid":105567,"like":20,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"8555e541aba99b21f4f52aaf736aea70db1724f2","tid":2197490,"uid":105567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T15:48:49.000Z","msg":"簡單來說，「沽空」是指你在出售股票時，並無持有該股票，但對有關股票擁有一項即時可行使而無條件的售賣權利。然而，並非所有股票均可沽空。<br />\n<br />\n哪些證券可沽空？<br />\n<br />\n目前，只有被聯交所列為「可進行賣空的指定證券」才可進行沽空。<br />\n<br />\n可進行賣空的指定證券名單如下：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkex.com.hk/Services/Trading/Securities/Securities-Lists/Designated-Securities-Eligible-for-Short-Selling?sc_lang=zh-HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkex.com.hk%2FServices%2FTrading%2FSecurities%2FSecurities-Lists%2FDesignated-Securities-Eligible-for-Short-Selling%3Fsc_lang%3Dzh-HK&d=u5s3JLQ1HZhTjCUFZ9m1FDizWcNDgH0nsvPDQhA%2BiAk%3D&h=5cc51628\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkex.com.hk/Services/Trading/Securities/Securities-Lists/Designated-Securities-Eligible-for-Short-Selling?sc_lang=zh-HK</a><br />\n<br />\n#你都識人哋低買高賣<br />\n#有貨嘅情況下賣又邊係沽空<br />\n#睇錢家有道學下理財知識先啦 顯示較少內容<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jbOjwxc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjbOjwxc.jpg&h=94fd3036&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ed11bd87bce815eb31d2ee699c0e53448a288462","tid":2197490,"uid":190281,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T15:55:54.000Z","msg":"股票 關毒品調查科咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我睇緊乜"},{"pid":"e66ea93bc3fdc3af09418fe81d03be9f30056210","tid":2197490,"uid":232845,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T15:59:59.000Z","msg":"撚有得沽空"},{"pid":"7b9a77e9990e30ae805ee09a665144f7b0a3f9b4","tid":2197490,"uid":129924,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T17:36:33.000Z","msg":"警謊都講左成年幾啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class